com.lightbend.lagom.javadsl.server.status

Class Latency.Builder

  • Object
    • com.lightbend.lagom.javadsl.server.status.Latency.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    Latency

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class Latency.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type Latency. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
